  "title": "Pixel's Client Mods",
  "description": "Client modifications to enhance vanilla gameplay on SMP servers. \nWARNING: Some mods on this list may be bannable on certain servers. Check with your specific server before playing.",
  "body": "Pixel's Client mods adds many customizable vanilla+ features, useful tools, and tweaks to the vanilla game, all without needing any mods to be installed on the server side. Pixel's Client Mods can be useful for everyone- from singleplayer worlds to SMP servers, but specifically focuses on more technical players, who want to get the most out of the game possible.\n\n### WARNING: Some mods on this list may be bannable on certain servers. Check with your server's staff before playing.\n\n<details><summary>Current Mod List</summary>\n\n### *This is not a complete list. Libraries and support mods are not included.*\n| Icon                                                                                                                           | Mod                            | Description/Use                         |\n|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------|-----------------------------------------|\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T9R7YTnA/287bd462ce813d2089beb0a436478b68c285e721.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/>    | TotemCounter                   | Helps you manage your totems.           |\n|                                                                                                                                | BadOptimizations               | Optimization Mod.                       |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/uXXizFIs/222a126f26f8f9ae1eb339f3b767677f18bff31f_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | FerriteCore                    | Optimization Mod (For Memory)           |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/UMxybHE8/4adf057a251f694983af139a06839e33bcd7a419.png\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/>     | MiniHUD                        | A Better way to use F3                  |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/VSNURh3q/3c2ce471054466712a44c8758a03e03bb868f93b_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | C2ME                           | Optimization Mod.                       |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/fJi8nm80/5ea9aeeb89e08524310ae9e6b71f793e2ba63e0f_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | ClickThrough Plus              | Stop Clicking on Signs!                 |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/zQxjhDPq/icon.png\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/>                                         | ChunkDebug                     | Finally see what chunks are doing       |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/qQyHxfxd/icon.png\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/>                                         | No Chat Reports                | Get those pesky reports out.            |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/8qkXwOnk/icon.png\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/>                                         | More Chat History              | It's in the name.                       |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/4I1XuqiY/6e5bbd0d06b1741bfdab6c0cfab6de8fdaf0064c_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | EMF                            | Entity Model Support                    |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/n6PXGAoM/c5a85914f01be35575abe61c2d19d48e08581034_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Better Statistics Screen       | Pretty self-explanatory.                |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/5ZwdcRci/e57b6b451425692ac17ad322d5e14bea686a383a_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | ImmediatelyFast                | Optimization Mod.                       |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/LQ3K71Q1/5056368d0d87c1a9f3efead0cb48ab39a4ea87bf_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Dynamic FPS                    | Reduce computer strain when not focused |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/vPNqo58Q/a9144fbd356f92c39be0e5b70d73136ac37fe0f6_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Client Tweaks                  | A Few Useful Tweaks.                    |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/M08ruV16/icon.png\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/>                                         | Bobby                          | Improves your render distance.          |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/MPCX6s5C/b97fd5f7a893165052408b747286d6eb38d57abb_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Not Enough Animations          | Add some animations to cool places.     |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/JygyCSA4/07db2203f74b2adc775822c2edf577b343df04f8_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | ItemScroller                   | A Nice way of using your inventory.     |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/7Coz83fv/76df7a8a5563f83c998be7ac8572964da59306c8_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | clientcommands                 | Some technical commands.                |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/NNAgCjsB/7873452d6cede4daed12da3d7d8c193ab88b4fd6_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Entity Culling                 | Stop rendering what's not in view!      |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/BVzZfTc1/af683d206d50b05258d865b0d6e4aa2f2cee12f2_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | ETF                            | Expanded entity texturing               |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/kYuIpRLv/a51c297bdaf9685a23cc9994372fa8d45852b98b_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Wavey Capes                    | Capes should wave!                      |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/ihnBJ6on/c200c6cb193f3d71c9041ea4ee746556689376fc_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Entity View Distance           | Tweak how far you need to see entities. |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/b1ZV3DIJ/3dec7dd828894a4c5c6d98eaf960e9a418647b55_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Athena                         | CTM                                     |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/qyVF9oeo/798fbfae58ec95ad51f3e1d522b43227306c326c.png\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/>     | Sound Physics Remastered       | Makes the game sound more realistic.    |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/QdG47OkI/5a8203e120985d11616614e11ad7b888997000d8.png\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/>     | Model Gap Fix                  | Yeah, those models need to be fixed.    |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/AANobbMI/295862f4724dc3f78df3447ad6072b2dcd3ef0c9_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Sodium                         | You know it, you love it.               |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/fQEb0iXm/3ea60899d060a9286e03b87bfa9e71d0cbe2dde7_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Krypton                        | Optimization mod.                       |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/TQTTVgYE/3ad650635d067b6bfa09403cf5e70e0947a05c07_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Carpet                         | Everything a technical player needs.    |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T6oqPfxF/6400c274d98a87ff8df6f128c1a12f1d1363cc5c_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Xaero Zoomout                  | You should be able to zoom out further. |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/N6n5dqoA/dd175669d5ac228dc00453d13528ad26c1f056ac.png\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/>     | Axiom                          | The ultimate building mod.              |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/Si9Uim4y/01f8bfb3455a5c13bdd8bc3402e4779ecf3b7bbe_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Detail Armor Bar Reconstructed | See what you're wearing.                |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/yBW8D80W/d4f5c3ff8df7caf024178b04eca6d69f95979cfe_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | LambDynamicLights              | Dynamic lighting.                       |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/ETlrkaYF/6c1711b4b788b5f25cc1e99ed8805aea94d9e167_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Cubes Without Borders          | Fullscreen mode made 100x better.       |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/jE0SjGuf/0eb2c1c34fee3c75e5fdadd7274d071445b80e9e_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Carpet TIS Addition            | Expansion to Carpet.                    |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/yjgIrBjZ/icon.png\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/>                                         | Auth Me                        | Keeps you logged in.                    |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/r0v8vy1s/fbb5a094676807df4b5ca1686033d5eb5fc389fd.png\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/>     | Alternate Current              | Makes Redstone perform well, finally.   |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/Bh37bMuy/icon.png\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/>                                         | Reese's Sodium Options         | Expanded sodium configuration.          |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/O7RBXm3n/04cdecd37b4c7409f70d36fcdc85722ebf14aab8_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Inventory Profiles Next        | Even better inventory management.       |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/t5wuYk45/35af76cfb1d3074c5e8575d5f7385bb6c083c9d6.png\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/>     | Tweakeroo                      | The best client-side tweaks.            |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/3qsfQtE9/icon.png\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/>                                         | Fabrishot                      | Makes your screenshots cool.            |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/gvQqBUqZ/bcc8686c13af0143adf4285d741256af824f70b7_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Lithium                        | Optimization Mod.                       |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/ZP7xHXtw/7a416b09817a79adfa6a3ef9368990135e276821_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Remove Reloading Screen        | Makes Pack Switching Better.            |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bEpr0Arc/25b5529d7a3b030ac136a6ce879d8ed2a1aa4a8d.png\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/>     | Litematica                     | Schematics!                             |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/GBeCx05I/1877e2ad70c2b4ef34ce77cd03eabb6531f476f8_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | TweakerMore                    | Expands Tweakeroo.                      |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/2M01OLQq/bb490716cf2590cf84100a495931c3d4743bce43_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Shulker Box Tooltip            | Have a little peak inside.              |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/51shyZVL/c51b07193b56e952269ef50101d12aecba2b4747_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | More Culling                   | What's in the camera is all I need.     |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/Wb5oqrBJ/icon.png\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/>                                         | Chat Heads                     | See who's chatting!                     |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/NcUtCpym/354080f65407e49f486fcf9c4580e82c45ae63b8_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Xaero's World Map              | See what's in the world.                |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/1bokaNcj/354080f65407e49f486fcf9c4580e82c45ae63b8_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Xaero's Minimap                | See what's around you.                  |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/RLzHAoZe/a353989ea9f0f124ebe7cf3e67274c2d72751431_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Resourcify                     | Resource pack updater.                  |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/KuNKN7d2/7490b4d8e08bde8df44b2a71774edf2fe3176c83_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Noisium                        | Optimization mod.                       |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/zV5r3pPn/ff7010d4ec0275609866c8b0f603b25e25949c08_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | 3D Skin Layers                 | Makes skins cooler.                     |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/ZcR9weSm/8da8af58ca961f937bd05d41dcefa26be7b5c182.png\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/>     | Dynamic Crosshair              | Makes your crosshair cool.              |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/rI0hvYcd/5c866549318e907bbfe0d525afe43cb17a36a481.png\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/>     | Visuality                      | Some more particles.                    |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/EsAfCjCV/icon.png\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/>                                         | AppleSkin                      | YOU'RE HUNGRY!                          |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/YL57xq9U/18d0e7f076d3d6ed5bedd472b853909aac5da202_96.webp\" alt=\"drawing\" width=\"50\"/> | Iris Shaders                   | Shaders are cool, kids.                 |\n</details>\n\nThe latest list of mods can be found [Here](https://modrinth.com/modpack/pixel-client-mods/version/0.0.3)\n\n*I Do not own nor develop any mods in this pack. I highly suggest supporting all the developers of the mods! They're all super cool for doing what they do.*",
